# German Law Vault — Zed Agent Rules

## Project Overview

**German Law Vault** provides a comprehensive search engine and AI-guided legal assistant for all German federal laws (>6,000 laws) from [gesetze-im-internet.de](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/).

**Architecture**: Next.js 16 (App Router) + Supabase (PostgreSQL) + Qdrant Cloud (vector search)

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Framework | Next.js | 16.2.9 |
| UI Library | React | 19.2.4 |
| Language | TypeScript | 5.x (strict mode) |
| Database | PostgreSQL (Supabase) | 17 |
| Vector Search | Qdrant Cloud | E5-small managed inference |
| Animation | motion | 12.40+ |
| Icons | lucide-react | latest |
| Validation | Zod | 4.4+ |
| Testing | Vitest | 4.1+ |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | 4.x |

